snippet.title: Chill beta test on Nov 15 — sign-up is live!!
snippet.description:
Kick back and relax
Kewlbiverse, an open-world pocket monster tamer, is launching a chill beta test on Nov 15!

▶  Sign up for the test!◀
November 8 at 3:00 AM to November 13 at 3:59 PM (UTC+0) 
•Official Website: kewlbi.com
•This test is for Android users only

See ya in #Kewlbiverse #chillCBT
